Class ContingentValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • Regularization.ContingentValue

  • public class ContingentValue
extends java.lang.Object
    First attribute is a 'Value' Expression that can be used to combine with that of other ConditionedValue; Second attribute, if any,will be a conjunctive clause that describes the condition of this 'value'. publicly it only accepts fixed order expression
